column5: Well guys,,,I did make it up to the boq on the weekend but unfortuantly i was not able to make it down to the g2g to meet all you fine folks,,,although rushed for time i did managege to get out for about four hours of fishing on saturday morning and ended up catching a nice walleye and a good size pike,,,forgot the camera so did not get any boat shots but did take a pic when i got home saturday night...like i said it was a short trip,,,but fun to get out anyway,,,hopeing to get one last musky run before the boat goes away for the hard water season!!
